# POS version capabilities

Branches may run older WellSale POS builds. Webadmin must not hard-require fields or APIs that only exist in newer apps.

## Rules

1. Before wiring a feature that depends on new POS behaviour, add/update an entry in `lib/app-capabilities.ts` with `minVersion`.
2. Gate UI with `branchSupports` / `summarizeCapability` and show `AppCapabilityNotice` when some branches are outdated.
3. Prefer empty states + soft notices over throwing or blocking the whole page when live/sync data is missing.
4. Never treat missing optional metadata (`cash_total`, `stock_after`, live TX, etc.) as a fatal error — fall back or show "—".
5. Subadmin must not resolve faults (`BranchFaults` `canResolve` only for mainadmin).

## Current gated features

- `livePosSync` / `liveStockMovements` — min `1.6.0` (cloud TX + stock tables)
